'''Edda Manga''' (born 1969)<ref>{{cite news |first=Edda |last=Manga |title=Edda Manga: Tillväxtens ideologi gör oss fattiga |url= http://www.gp.se/kulturnoje/1.372125-edda-manga-tillvaxtens-ideologi-gor-oss-fattiga |publisher=Göteborgs-Posten |date=2004-09-14 |accessdate=2010-05-19 |language=Swedish}}</ref> is a [[Swedish people|Swedish]] [[History of ideas|historian of ideas]], speaker and debator. Manga won the [[Clioprize]] in 2004 for her [[Thesis or dissertation|doctorate thesis]] ''Gudomliga uppenbarelser och demoniska samlag'' ("Divine revelations and demonic intercourses").<ref>{{cite news |first=Eva |last=Bäckstedt |title=Historisk onani ledde till Cliopris |url= http://www.svd.se/kulturnoje/nyheter/historisk-onani-ledde-till-cliopris_163430.svd |publisher=Svenska Dagbladet |date=2004-09-14 |accessdate=2010-10-17 |language=Swedish}}</ref> She was a summer host on [[Sveriges Radio P1]] during ''Sommar i P1'' on 14 June 2004.<ref>{{cite web | url = http://sverigesradio.se/sida/artikel.aspx?programid=3421&artikel=860986 | title = Sommarvärdar 2004 | work = Sveriges Radio | accessdate = 2010-10-17 }}</ref> In 2011 she together with her husband was a speaker at the summer camp of the [[Communist Party (Sweden)|Communist Party]] in Sweden, though she is not a member.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.kommunisterna.org/nyheter/2011/08/kommunisternas-sommarlager|title=Kommunisternas sommarläger|last=admin|date=2011-08-04|website=www.kommunisterna.org|language=sv|access-date=2017-12-25}}</ref>Since January 2016 she works as a researcher at Mångkulturellt centrum (tr: [[Multiculturalism|Multicultural]] center).<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://mkcentrum.se/edda-manga/|title=Edda Manga - Mångkulturellt Centrum|work=Mångkulturellt Centrum|access-date=2017-12-25|language=sv-SE}}</ref> Edda Manga is active in public debates and is a defender of Muslim women in Sweden to wear the [[hijab]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.gp.se/nyheter/debatt/samma-gamla-slitna-pamflett-om-sl%C3%B6jan-1.3995|title=Samma gamla slitna pamflett om slöjan|work=Göteborgs-Posten|access-date=2017-12-25|language=sv}}</ref> She has in turn been criticised for trivialising the issue of women as victims of [[Honor culture#Sweden|violent honor cultures]] in Sweden.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.gp.se/ledare/f%C3%B6rnekarna-av-hedersv%C3%A5ld-1.4375211|title=Förnekarna av hedersvåld|work=Göteborgs-Posten|access-date=2017-12-25|language=sv}}</ref>
